Titolo: Ghost Whisperer (video game)

Anno: 2012

Descrizione: Ghost Whisperer is a casual hidden-object mystery adventure game developed by Legacy Games for Microsoft Windows and Mac OS. The game is based on the CBS supernatural television drama Ghost Whisperer starring Melinda Gordon (Jennifer Love Hewitt). The game contains two different cases to solve: "Forgotten Toys" and "A Brush with Death".